{"type": "article", "id": 9778, "title": "hsbLABS 平面变立体", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-20T07:12:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 21, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606152502MHK82rhdUqQsB0PN.png", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">hsbCAD 工作室最近推出了一个可以帮助建筑设计师把平面设计方案变为 3D 立体模型的应用程序，名字叫做 “hsbLABS”。他们使用应用程序，将建筑草图分解成不同的部分，再通过3D打印机打印出来之后进行拼接。这款程序不需要其他的用具辅助，只需打印材料和颜料，便可以打印出立体的 3D 建筑模板。<a href=\"http://www.hsblabs.com/#target\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152459k9tvyVs84haWr07L.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.52689487\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152500edW5xHQi3FJYrpcj.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.5391198\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152500vzNtxMhkD2Eem5Or.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.53789731\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152500VKZLjyOTd7ISpaw2.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.54156479\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152501qWfXwiS4GHKzZmh7.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.48899756\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><br>\r\n</span>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}